{"tid":140213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獲CNN推薦　不敵貴租結業","createTime":"2017-03-02T04:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T10:53:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6e8fd012dd1b59f6874f0cd42cc2e8c6ebd0f2e","tid":140213,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:30:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170302/19944849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170302%2F19944849&d=CmeYdDJU3P8b8ZKgyBn5o54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f25934c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170302%2F19944849&h=53af5965\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170302/19944849</a><br />\n<br />\n獲CNN推薦　不敵貴租結業<br />\n<br />\n12,267<br />\n ■13座牛雜。<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n■13座牛雜。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】13座牛雜憑獨門滷水汁成為街知巷聞小食店，其牛雜於2010年獲CNN評為「香港不可缺少的40美食」之一。成為地標小食店後，13座牛雜開始擴充業務，先後在大坑、灣仔及將軍澳等地設分店，最終因不敵貴租及難請人，連有近10年歷史的北角總店也要結業。<br />\n<br />\n轉戰台灣亦碰壁<br />\n其中一名合夥人湯建業其後轉戰台灣，於2014年在台北士林夜市重開13座牛雜，大受當地人歡迎，然而由於貨源不穩和經營困難，在去年10月底暫停營業，湯建業當時在facebook表示若找到穩妥貨源便會重新開業。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，13座牛雜的名字來自第一代創始人湯良初，亦即湯建業父親。40多年前湯爸爸專賣牛雜的小販車固定停泊屋邨第13座，街坊都稱呼為第13座牛雜。湯於2005年與其他人合夥重開父業，13座牛雜在北角新光戲院旁開店。於2014年結業前，牛雜售價為一串10元、細盒40元、大盒60元，但仍不敵月租4.9萬元。<br />\n<br />\n■記者歐陽聯發  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n13座牛雜老闆洗黑錢逾億　稱為拍檔兄弟開戶還柙候懲<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n舊同事涉賄蘋果員工收iPhone鬼機"},{"pid":"39da225c716b0a8aa23aaed895af56f087ba227e","tid":140213,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:31:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170302/large/02la7p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170302%2Flarge%2F02la7p2.jpg&h=9d0cfc9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b36544bd92f65e42fdaa5b8090952dec2473dbbc","tid":140213,"uid":84585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:36:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1efbf30e5198ca34ff9b2308cc0f8fe7dea05548","tid":140213,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"去台灣都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbac93c1cfb6498076da79091efdce8bb35c21e","tid":140213,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"上一則新聞就係講老闆洗黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8b97c2af95b33a8a8538171cb558a5e50c78f3","tid":140213,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"業主係咪有病。 佢租個位俾人做生意收人 出錢出力既價錢。"},{"pid":"3b11dd61a0b152f0152c7656e9fb2c6a14db5edc","tid":140213,"uid":34184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:06:42.000Z","msg":"巔峯期有5間分店，營業額每年平均60至70萬元，可惜因為不敵租金<br />\n<br />\n700,000/12/5=11,666.66<br />\n<br />\n營業額額咁細,仲夠膽開咁多間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7f0bc7f08b069b616d605bdbb2fea6b3af747a","tid":140213,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:41:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上一則新聞就係講老闆洗黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n華生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948b6b9aeb541124e06bfc54743fd4f68b9b35ed","tid":140213,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巔峯期有5間分店，營業額每年平均60至70萬元，可惜因為不敵租金<br />\n<br />\n700,000/12/5=11,666.66<br />\n<br />\n營業額額咁細,仲夠膽開咁多間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但洗黑錢成億"},{"pid":"2f96d0677af27cfbd650b03860c2f90439c0250b","tid":140213,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:11:32.000Z","msg":"